{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>CodeIgniter is an Application Development Framework - a toolkit - for people who build web sites using PHP.\nIts goal is to enable you to develop projects much faster than you could if you were writing code from scratch, by providing a rich set of libraries for commonly needed tasks, as well as a simple interface and logical structure to access these libraries.\nCodeIgniter lets you creatively focus on your project by minimizing the amount of code needed for a given task.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"2016-10-15","title":"CodeIgniter","tags":["CodeIgniter"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.6942857142857144,"src":"/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/15450/CodeIgniter.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/df0d1/CodeIgniter.jpg 480w,\n/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/1e858/CodeIgniter.jpg 960w,\n/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/15450/CodeIgniter.jpg 1186w","srcWebp":"/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/a4c1d/CodeIgniter.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/2ef77/CodeIgniter.webp 480w,\n/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/cce33/CodeIgniter.webp 960w,\n/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/a4c1d/CodeIgniter.webp 1186w","sizes":"(max-width: 1186px) 100vw, 1186px"},"resize":{"src":"/static/9f92ff36255fa6da7f695386fbe1fe4a/d260a/CodeIgniter.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"pathSlug":"/codeigniter","prev":null,"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/laravel","title":"Laravel","tags":["laravel","other"]}}}}